title: MFA Press Statement: Introductory Visit of Minister for Foreign Affairs Dr Vivian Balakrishnan to Negara ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Singapore ) Minister for Foreign Affairs Dr Vivian Balakrishnan will begin his introductory visits to the region with a visit to Negara Brunei Darussalam from 25 to 26 October 2015 .
